<sect1 id="gomenu">
<title>The Go Menu</title>
<para>In this menu you find actions to navigate between the sheets of the currently 
opened spreadsheet and the <guimenuitem>Goto Cell</guimenuitem> action to jump to a single 
cell or to select a range of cells.</para>
</sect1>

