<listitem><para><action>Choose the color theme for &sheets; window.</action> You can choose
one of the predefined color schemes or select <guimenuitem>Configuration...</guimenuitem> to
open <ulink url="help:/kcontrol/colors">&systemsettings; color selection module</ulink>.
</para></listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term><menuchoice>
<guimenu>Settings</guimenu>
