</menuchoice></term>
<listitem><para><action>Configure the author profile for the current document.</action> You can choose
one of the profiles defined using <link linkend="configauthor">&sheets; configuration window</link>,
<guimenuitem>Default Author Profile</guimenuitem> as defined by &systemsettings; data or
